That's a great question.

00:18:36.380 --> 00:18:36.910 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:18:36.910 --> 00:18:37.410 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:18:37.410 --> 00:18:41.140 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: This question is
applicable to all the people

00:18:41.140 --> 00:18:44.370 align:middle line:84%
whom I have great respect
for, who also reached

00:18:44.370 --> 00:18:46.630 align:middle line:84%
a very high level
of enlightenment.

