But then, they did not know
how to deal with the body.

00:18:50.770 --> 00:18:53.380 align:middle line:84%
So to me, the
enlightenment is not just

00:18:53.380 --> 00:18:57.520 align:middle line:84%
simply for the mind, or
psychological enlightenment.

00:18:57.520 --> 00:18:58.710 align:middle line:90%
It's still an enlightenment.

00:18:58.710 --> 00:19:01.190 align:middle line:84%
You'll be liberated
from your thoughts.

00:19:01.190 --> 00:19:04.540 align:middle line:84%
So you will not be
bothered by the thoughts.

