or lose your belongings.

00:19:12.310 --> 00:19:13.500 align:middle line:90%
That will not bother you.

00:19:13.500 --> 00:19:15.400 align:middle line:84%
So you're psychologically
liberated,

00:19:15.400 --> 00:19:16.380 align:middle line:90%
which is pretty good.

00:19:16.380 --> 00:19:17.980 align:middle line:90%


00:19:17.980 --> 00:19:20.950 align:middle line:84%
You can, again, get a
thought whenever you want.

00:19:20.950 --> 00:19:23.890 align:middle line:84%
And then if you don't want a
thought, you can push it out.

00:19:23.890 --> 00:19:26.110 align:middle line:84%
So that kind of a
liberty will be there.

00:19:26.110 --> 00:19:29.211 align:middle line:84%
But still, with regard to
the body of your cancer,

00:19:29.211 --> 00:19:30.210 align:middle line:90%
then you will have pain.

00:19:30.210 --> 00:19:31.970 align:middle line:90%


00:19:31.970 --> 00:19:33.986 align:middle line:90%
That you cannot avoid.

00:19:33.986 --> 00:19:34.610 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Really?

00:19:34.610 --> 00:19:35.193 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yes.

