For that, what you need to
do is-- you may be like,

00:19:39.070 --> 00:19:43.330 align:middle line:84%
you know, I was very closely
associated with Norman Cousins.

00:19:43.330 --> 00:19:45.110 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Oh really, yes.

00:19:45.110 --> 00:19:47.080 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: And then he
was here in Los Angeles.

00:19:47.080 --> 00:19:50.820 align:middle line:84%
And then he was
starting this center

00:19:50.820 --> 00:19:55.190 align:middle line:84%
called Psychoneuroimmunology
for the medial school here.

00:19:55.190 --> 00:19:56.320 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: At UCLA, yes.

