It'll still be pain, and
I can somewhat control it.

00:20:16.810 --> 00:20:22.890 align:middle line:84%
When somebody comes with axe,
then I have to really give up.

00:20:22.890 --> 00:20:24.150 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK, I understand.

00:20:24.150 --> 00:20:24.650 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:20:24.650 --> 00:20:26.320 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: So that was
an example that he gave.

00:20:26.320 --> 00:20:26.960 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: I see.

00:20:26.960 --> 00:20:29.620 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: So you
cannot take it too far.

00:20:29.620 --> 00:20:32.710 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: You cannot just
disintegrate into dust.

00:20:32.710 --> 00:20:35.196 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: The body is
so real, that's why

00:20:35.196 --> 00:20:38.106 align:middle line:84%
it is very important to
turn the body into light.

00:20:38.106 --> 00:20:39.230 align:middle line:90%
And this is not impossible.

00:20:39.230 --> 00:20:40.310 align:middle line:90%


00:20:40.310 --> 00:20:42.985 align:middle line:84%
Because we are now
living at a time,

00:20:42.985 --> 00:20:45.510 align:middle line:84%
on the earth plane,
where the earth plane

00:20:45.510 --> 00:20:47.890 align:middle line:90%
itself is ready for that.

00:20:47.890 --> 00:20:51.810 align:middle line:84%
Until now, it has not happened,
because the earth plane has--

00:20:51.810 --> 00:20:54.050 align:middle line:84%
mother earth has been
preparing herself

00:20:54.050 --> 00:20:56.310 align:middle line:90%
to evolve become a light planet.

00:20:56.310 --> 00:20:58.080 align:middle line:90%
It is a dense planet, now.

00:20:58.080 --> 00:21:00.890 align:middle line:84%
That's why we are living here,
it only vibrates at 8 hertz.

00:21:00.890 --> 00:21:02.070 align:middle line:90%


00:21:02.070 --> 00:21:04.990 align:middle line:90%
So that's the reality.

00:21:04.990 --> 00:21:06.480 align:middle line:90%
It's a very low reality.

00:21:06.480 --> 00:21:09.155 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Why do you say this
is a specific time for this?

00:21:09.155 --> 00:21:09.780 align:middle line:90%
What's changed?

00:21:09.780 --> 00:21:11.620 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: When the
Mayan calendar changed.

00:21:11.620 --> 00:21:12.286 align:middle line:90%
They were right.

00:21:12.286 --> 00:21:13.510 align:middle line:90%


00:21:13.510 --> 00:21:18.310 align:middle line:84%
The civilization ended, and a
new civilization has started.

00:21:18.310 --> 00:21:19.850 align:middle line:90%
Not the world ending.

00:21:19.850 --> 00:21:21.880 align:middle line:84%
A new civilization
has started, that we

00:21:21.880 --> 00:21:24.040 align:middle line:84%
are more open to
ideas like this.

00:21:24.040 --> 00:21:27.240 align:middle line:84%
That's why we have quantum
physics coming and Eisenberg

00:21:27.240 --> 00:21:30.060 align:middle line:84%
