We are living in a world
of complete possibilities.

00:21:41.480 --> 00:21:45.760 align:middle line:84%
So this is the new education
that we need to learn.

00:21:45.760 --> 00:21:47.327 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: He was a true visionary.

00:21:47.327 --> 00:21:47.910 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yes.

00:21:47.910 --> 00:21:50.570 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Yes, he said that
in such a time of density--

00:21:50.570 --> 00:21:51.370 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yeah.

