That's the problem.

00:21:53.790 --> 00:21:56.690 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Do you think we're
getting closer to the light?

00:21:56.690 --> 00:21:57.300 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yes.

00:21:57.300 --> 00:21:58.055 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: You do.

00:21:58.055 --> 00:21:58.680 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yeah.

00:21:58.680 --> 00:22:01.680 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And do you think that
we can manifest our own healing

00:22:01.680 --> 00:22:03.629 align:middle line:90%
using that concept of light?

00:22:03.629 --> 00:22:04.420 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yes, yes.

00:22:04.420 --> 00:22:05.010 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: We can.

00:22:05.010 --> 00:22:05.635 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yeah.

00:22:05.635 --> 00:22:06.500 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: How?

00:22:06.500 --> 00:22:13.260 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: See, we now
live with the conviction,

00:22:13.260 --> 00:22:20.510 align:middle line:84%
