of this logical mind

00:22:25.050 --> 00:22:29.540 align:middle line:84%
and then live in a field
of all possibilities,

00:22:29.540 --> 00:22:30.690 align:middle line:90%
then everything happens.

00:22:30.690 --> 00:22:33.370 align:middle line:84%
Because everything
that you see is

00:22:33.370 --> 00:22:36.170 align:middle line:84%
only a reflection
of whatever inner.

00:22:36.170 --> 00:22:37.960 align:middle line:90%
So the inner is the outer.

00:22:37.960 --> 00:22:40.020 align:middle line:90%
That's the bottom line.

00:22:40.020 --> 00:22:45.300 align:middle line:84%
So that's why I tell people that
if you see poverty everywhere,

00:22:45.300 --> 00:22:51.140 align:middle line:84%
