of my techniques.

00:24:58.650 --> 00:24:59.700 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Many times.

00:24:59.700 --> 00:25:01.080 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yeah, the techniques.

00:25:01.080 --> 00:25:03.130 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: He was the one
that introduced me to you.

00:25:03.130 --> 00:25:04.980 align:middle line:90%
And so you can take these--

00:25:04.980 --> 00:25:08.740 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: One day, I
met him in Chicago.

00:25:08.740 --> 00:25:11.070 align:middle line:84%
