Beyond the clouds,
the sun is shining.

00:25:24.920 --> 00:25:25.460 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:25:25.460 --> 00:25:26.430 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: So that's the truth.

00:25:26.430 --> 00:25:27.126 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:25:27.126 --> 00:25:27.694 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:25:27.694 --> 00:25:29.110 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: The sun
is always there.

00:25:29.110 --> 00:25:30.050 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Always there.

00:25:30.050 --> 00:25:31.508 align:middle line:84%
You get in an
airplane, it's there.

00:25:31.508 --> 00:25:32.590 align:middle line:90%


00:25:32.590 --> 00:25:34.850 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: He appreciated
that very much.

00:25:34.850 --> 00:25:36.230 align:middle line:90%
He said that was a great thing.

00:25:36.230 --> 00:25:41.180 align:middle line:84%
And when I read that I really
felt the truth behind it.

00:25:41.180 --> 00:25:44.310 align:middle line:90%


00:25:44.310 --> 00:25:46.300 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Back to the
idea of the intention.

00:25:46.300 --> 00:25:48.570 align:middle line:84%
And from what Wayne
wrote his book on,

00:25:48.570 --> 00:25:52.510 align:middle line:84%
the power of intention, you
can manifest this thought,

00:25:52.510 --> 00:25:55.030 align:middle line:84%
and you can turn
it into a reality.

00:25:55.030 --> 00:25:56.060 align:middle line:90%
>>PILLAI: Yes, yes.

00:25:56.060 --> 00:25:58.330 align:middle line:84%
So that's exactly the
book that he wrote,

00:25:58.330 --> 00:25:59.815 align:middle line:90%
which he dedicated to me.

00:25:59.815 --> 00:26:03.000 align:middle line:84%
It's called "Manifest
Your Destiny."

00:26:03.000 --> 00:26:07.670 align:middle line:84%
And the thesis point in that
book is what I gave him,

00:26:07.670 --> 00:26:11.445 align:middle line:84%
