which you cannot conceive.

00:26:11.445 --> 00:26:13.740 align:middle line:90%


00:26:13.740 --> 00:26:16.326 align:middle line:84%
You cannot manifest that
you cannot conceive.

00:26:16.326 --> 00:26:17.410 align:middle line:90%


00:26:17.410 --> 00:26:21.610 align:middle line:84%
For instance, I can easily
conceive a million dollars,

00:26:21.610 --> 00:26:22.852 align:middle line:90%
and I can manifest it.

00:26:22.852 --> 00:26:24.810 align:middle line:84%
A couple of million
dollars, I can manifest it.

00:26:24.810 --> 00:26:27.430 align:middle line:84%
Then I cannot conceal
of a billion dollars.

00:26:27.430 --> 00:26:28.770 align:middle line:90%


00:26:28.770 --> 00:26:31.380 align:middle line:84%
The day when I am able to
conceive a billion dollar,

00:26:31.380 --> 00:26:33.330 align:middle line:84%
