even a $5,000.

00:26:39.720 --> 00:26:41.840 align:middle line:84%
So the problem is
the conception.

00:26:41.840 --> 00:26:43.600 align:middle line:90%


00:26:43.600 --> 00:26:45.970 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: If they don't have
any education or any prior

00:26:45.970 --> 00:26:46.470 align:middle line:90%
example--

00:26:46.470 --> 00:26:48.095 align:middle line:84%
>>PILLAI: You don't
need any education.

00:26:48.095 --> 00:26:49.340 align:middle line:90%


00:26:49.340 --> 00:26:51.300 align:middle line:84%
Academic education,
you don't need.

00:26:51.300 --> 00:26:55.300 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: But example, or mentor,
or any idea of an example

00:26:55.300 --> 00:26:58.562 align:middle line:84%
